abstract="In this paper, we propose an approach of activity context integration as a means of evaluating semantic information, by integrating situational information from heterogeneous sensors in a smartphone. The proposed activity context integration is a method to provide a foundation for interacting with situation-aware mobile computing systems. Moreover, we develop a context-aware embedded middleware that generates high-level integrated contexts through the fusion of internal {\textbullet} external sensors in a smartphone. The proposed system extracts semantic information such as the user's activities.",
